    "description": "本課程內容由設計的本質談起，介紹各類設計領域與重要設計議題。主要的目的在於建立學生正確的設計概念，以奠定日後學習設計領域的良好基礎。<br>The content of course begins with the nature of design and introduces various design areas and important design issues.<br>The purpose is to establish the correct design concept for students to lay a good foundation for learning design in the future.<br>",
