        "zh": "(1)設計領域<br>(2)產品設計<br>(3)視覺傳達設計<br>(4)數位媒體設計<br>(5)空間設計<br>(6)設計史<br>(7)文化創意設計<br>(8)綠色設計 <br>(9)通用設計 <br>(10)感性設計<br>(11)未來設計思維發展",
        "en": "(1) About Design <br>(2) Product design<br>(3) visual communication design<br>(4) Digital media design<br>(5) Space design<br>(6) Design history<br>(7) Cultural and creative design<br>(8) Green design<br>(9) Universal design<br>(10) Sensible design<br>(11) Future design thinking development<br>"
